title: 116.70 DEFINITIONS.
text:
The definitions in this section apply to sections 116.731 to 116.734.
[Repealed, 1Sp2001 c 2 s 162]
"Chlorofluorocarbons" or "CFCs" means the substances identified as class I or class II substances under section 602 of the Clean Air Act, United States Code, title 42, section 7401 et seq., as amended by the Clean Air Act Amendments of 1990, Public Law 101-549.
